# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
# dist/ is built by `pnpm build` before `go build`; the //go:embed directive
# in embed.go picks it up from disk. We commit dist/.gitkeep (which is why
# the whole dir is not gitignored) so a fresh clone's `go build ./...` still
# compiles — you just won't see the SPA until you actually build the bundle.
dist/assets
dist/index.html
dist/favicon.svg
dist-ssr
*.local

